In [5]:
total_dice_all, total_dice_hard_all, total_iou_all = 0, 0, 0
total_dice_core, total_dice_hard_core, total_iou_core = 0, 0, 0
total_dice_enhance, total_dice_hard_enhance, total_iou_enhance = 0, 0, 0


for i in range(num):    
    seg_path, ground_path = get_patient_ground(i)
    print(seg_path, ground_path[67:])
    seg, ground = load(seg_path)[0], load(ground_path)[0]
   # print(seg.shape, ground.shape)
   # seg = np.transpose(seg, (1,0,2))
    dice, dice_hard, iou =  diceCheck(seg,ground, task='all')
    print ('all:')
    print('dice:', dice, 'dice_hard:', dice_hard, 'iou:', iou) 
    total_dice_all += dice
    total_dice_hard_all += dice_hard
    total_iou_all += iou
    dice, dice_hard, iou =  diceCheck(seg,ground, task='core')
    print ('core:')
    print('dice:', dice, 'dice_hard:', dice_hard, 'iou:', iou)
    total_dice_core += dice
    total_dice_hard_core += dice_hard
    total_iou_core += iou    
    dice, dice_hard, iou =  diceCheck(seg,ground, task='enhance')
    print ('enhance:')
    print('dice:', dice, 'dice_hard:', dice_hard, 'iou:', iou)
    total_dice_enhance += dice
    total_dice_hard_enhance += dice_hard
    total_iou_enhance += iou    
print('avg_dice_all:', total_dice_all/num, 'avg_dice_hard_all:', total_dice_hard_all/num, 
      'avg_iou_all:', total_iou_all/num)
print('avg_dice_core:', total_dice_core/num, 'avg_dice_hard_core:', total_dice_hard_core/num, 
      'avg_iou_core:', total_iou_core/num)    
print('avg_dice_enhance:', total_dice_enhance/num, 'avg_dice_hard_enhance:', total_dice_hard_enhance/num, 
      'avg_iou_enhance:', total_iou_enhance/num)
